{"tid":1302812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-07-10T05:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T16:52:11.000Z","uid":167355,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5692a02af3b5383de6c918fbd390da5bf64e7db0","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"無論你光復上水 <br />\n沙田遊行 <br />\n抵制TVB<br />\n參選區議會都好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1️⃣『撤回』修訂條例</span><br />\n無論政府用乜四字詞語 乜野同義詞 乜暫緩<br />\n我們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只接受『撤回』二字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2️⃣撤銷612暴動定性</span><br />\n無論政府講乜 總之所有檢控<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有「暴動罪」</span></span><br />\n破壞法治係政府 冇暴動定性 點會有暴動罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3️⃣成立獨立委員會</span><br />\n我地並非針對警方執法 <br />\n如前終審法院首席法官李國能所講<br />\n我地希望<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">調查</span></span>整件事既<span style=\"color: red;\">「前因後果」</span><br />\n現時<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">監警會</span></span>若市民投訴 可能會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">原告變被告</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4️⃣釋放被捕人士</span><br />\n我地同為香港人 如果要拉就檢控曬200萬人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有</span>一人可以被抽出來<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殺雞儆猴！</span><br />\n法理不外乎人情 法治精神 不可成為政府棋子<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5️⃣香港實施雙普選</span><br />\n每一個議員 每位特首 都要由自己選出來<br />\n因為我相信我地會為我地既票負責！不論如何<br />\n<br />\n大家 兄弟姊妹 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好比任何事</span>糢糊我地焦點！<br />\n我地有60幾位手足被捕<br />\n有好多人絕食抗爭<br />\n有好多人放棄生命 為左喚醒更多人！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Let <span style=\"color: red;\">Hong kong </span>be <span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong kong </span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我不做善忘人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n如果你同意 請推置頂！"},{"pid":"bcb4af1e3787d402af609a1386560ea7953b9c4c","tid":1302812,"uid":269203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e02f8948599c2ce26e7f5755c891b662f07c0d35","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac1d721455c5f2d9d94ddf1d49b151996e8f0732","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"我一直講 po左咁耐 冇人推<br />\n香港人就是善忘"},{"pid":"680598a3e1a20de04b70b9b273bad216a42e2a89","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"白色恐怖 唔記得左"},{"pid":"5ffd65aa2b3383e0226f1f6f20a9b200770c2e2a","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"612比人打到頭破血流 唔記得左"},{"pid":"9f70e8a172fbc03a7f0da43a31ba93c386394db3","tid":1302812,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:34:02.000Z","msg":"好失望"},{"pid":"fe1fac82c021d6d3cd141b985be4b05ac69fccbe","tid":1302812,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:31:07.000Z","msg":"贊成！推！"},{"pid":"3d34b0f139f666fdae878d263b28e42cf01f723e","tid":1302812,"uid":93994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"91c37c45242d4654258874896f2f8b2e605677f6","tid":1302812,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ceac7ea65d6f97cb3cb31d559cd645370b6c3ae","tid":1302812,"uid":191989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed285ada117269496a4f0dc2906970e7a6e6b24e","tid":1302812,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:18:20.000Z","msg":"push